It looks just like that.

00:00:30.030 --> 00:00:32.640
y equals x.

00:00:32.640 --> 00:00:36.700
And what I care about
now is the solid

00:00:36.700 --> 00:00:42.570
I get if I were to rotate the
area between these two things

00:00:42.570 --> 00:00:44.932
